Package: grainscape
Type: Package
Title: Grains of connectivity and minimum planar graph modelling of landscape connectivity
Description: Given a landscape resistance surface, creates grains of connectivity
  and minimum planar graph models that can be used to calculate effective distances
  for landscape connectivity at multiple scales. This is a cross-platform reimplementation
  of the `grainscape` package (https://r-forge.r-project.org/projects/grainscape/).
URL: https://github.com/achubaty/grainscape2
Version: 0.3.0.9000
Date: 2016-07-06
Authors@R: c(
