)
License: GPL (>= 2)
Depends:
  igraph,
  sp,
  raster
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.12.5)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Suggests:
  parallel,
  rgeos
VignetteBuilder: knitr, rmarkdown
